-- Goldman Cuts Three-Month Copper Price Target to $6,800 Vs. $8,125 a Ton
-- Glenys Sim
-- 2010-06-22T00:27:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/goldman-cuts-three-month-copper-price-target-to-6-800-vs-8-125-a-ton.html

          
          
             Goldman Sachs Group Inc. lowered its
three-month price forecasts for copper, aluminum and zinc on
weaker near-term fundamentals.  
